videos.title: The Meme That Broke Magic
videos.description:
It might have taken a decade, but here's the story about how Magic's biggest meme finally got its revenge and broke the game!

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish
